I tried removing the line and it looks okay. I might be reading this wrong but I think when we call `CheckTxInputs` with the `GetSpendHeight(view)`:
```c
if (!Consensus::CheckTxInputs(tx, state, view, GetSpendHeight(view), *fee_out)) {
```

[`GetSpendHeight()`](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/8aa3a4a498742dc42631956ed3599b3fb2b80302/src/validation.cpp#L1477) calls `GetBestBlock()` for `view` as well:

```c 
int GetSpendHeight(const CCoinsViewCache& inputs)
{
    LOCK(cs_main);
    CBlockIndex* pindexPrev = LookupBlockIndex(inputs.GetBestBlock());
    return pindexPrev->nHeight + 1;
}
```

